hopobject.body: What's the exchange rate for euros? amica-farmacia.com How would you feel if you returned home from a pleasant stroll to find a criminal standing in your home, laden with all manner of your possessions? Probably just a tad peeved. We speak to the lady who came across just such a scene but, instead of calling the police, took the desperate drug addict to her local church and provided him with a meal. Astonishing show of compassion. The baddie still got jailed though. Don’t miss the full story.
